---
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---
<PageLayout
  title="The Faceless Income Blueprint™ — Free Guide"
  description="Get the free Faceless Income Blueprint™ — the entire faceless income machine on one page, plus a simple way to find exactly where you're stuck."
>
  <div class="page-eyebrow">Free Resource</div>
  <h1>The Faceless Income Blueprint™</h1>
  <p class="lede">The entire faceless income machine, on one page — so you can stop collecting tips and start building.</p>

  <p>You've saved the reels. You've bookmarked the guides. You know it's possible — you've watched ordinary women do it — but every time you sit down to actually build, something's missing.</p>

  <p>That's not a laziness problem. It's a structure problem. This free guide puts the entire faceless income machine in front of you on a single page, so you can finally see how the pieces connect — and exactly where <em>you're</em> personally stuck.</p>

  <p><strong>Inside, you'll get:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>The two-engine framework every faceless business runs on</li>
    <li>A simple way to diagnose your own bottleneck</li>
    <li>The exact order to build in, so you stop spinning your wheels</li>
  </ul>

  <form style="display:flex;gap:12px;max-width:420px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:40px 0" onsubmit="return false">
    <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" aria-label="Email address"
      style="flex:1;min-width:220px;padding:16px 22px;border:1px solid var(--taupe);border-radius:100px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;background:var(--white);color:var(--choc)" />
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Send Me the Blueprint <span class="a">→</span></button>
  </form>

  <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--taupe)">Free, no spam, unsubscribe anytime. You'll also get our weekly newsletter — practical tutorials on AI, Pinterest, and digital products.</p>

  <p style="margin-top:60px"><a href="/learn" style="color:var(--pink);font-weight:500">← Back to The Library</a></p>
</PageLayout>
